<p style="text-align: center;" mce_style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva;" mce_style="font-family: trebuchet ms,geneva;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" mce_style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #008000;" mce_style="color: #008000;"><b>"Authentic  Middle Eastern Food Since 1972"</b></span></span></span></p>
